    "Title": "VIP Client Needs Protection",
    "Description": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Escort Ship\nApproval code: = ~mission(ApprovalCode)\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nIn need of a contractor who can report in now. A client has found themselves in hot water over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and a protection detail to get away from an asteroid base. They\u2019ve reported multiple, well-armed hostile ships meaning you\u2019ll need a crew of your own to deal with them. Based on the client\u2019s account, these attackers seem highly motivated so they will likely not back down easily.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
